title: Ergo Magnet™ Microfiber Flip Floor Duster
description: Ergo Magnet™ Microfiber Flip Floor Duster
transcripts: it's easy to replace the refill simply pull apart the velcro fasteners and slip the microfiber head over the gray plastic mop head to put your new refill on simply put the new microfiber refill over the gray mop head and fasten the velcro holders the ergonomic pole helps minimize physical effort by allowing you to get underneath furniture without bending the Duster head flips for two-sided microfiber cleaning the fluffy softer side is perfect for dusting floors and the textured side has scrubby ridges for cleaning dirtier grimier floors to care for your refill simply machine wash the microfiber head separately in warm water on delicate cycle do not use fabric softener. Air dry.
